Amar'e Stoudemire

Pronunciation: \ah-mahr-AY\

Amar'e Carsares Stoudemire

(S.T.A.T., The Little Tyrant, Little Lord)

Position: Power Forward and Center ▪ Shoots: Right

6-10, 245lb (208cm, 111kg)

Born: November 16, 1982 in Lake Wales, Florida us

High Schools: Lake Wales in Lake Wales, Florida, Mt. Zion Christian Academy in Durham, North Carolina, Emmanuel Christian Academy in Durham, North Carolina, West Orange in Winter Garden, Florida - attended but did not play, Cypress Creek in Orlando, Florida

Recruiting Rank: 2002 (1)

Draft: Phoenix Suns, 1st round (9th pick, 9th overall), 2002 NBA Draft

NBA Debut: October 30, 2002

Career Length: 14 years
